{
  "stem": "19969.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Almost six months we were stymied there until we built up enough strength to finally crack that Gustav Line in, oh, early May of 1944.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was a captain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a rifle company commander.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had Company E of the 157th Infantry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was wounded in Italy very seriously, an abdominal wound, which got part of my liver.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was in a hospital for, oh, over a month in North Africa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, I was wounded in late October and did not return until December of '43.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From there on then, I was a rifle company commander, up until and including the Invasion of Anzio.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A decision was made to try to take Rome by landing near Rome at a small port town called Anzio.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And our division, along with the 3rd Infantry Division and two British divisions, were given a task of making that landing and taking Rome.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We landed, but we didn't take Rome, not for several months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A shell fragment.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of the casualties during the war were caused by artillery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Artillery is the biggest casualty-producing agent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, the obvious reason is when a shell lands a, a reasonable distance from someone, that shell fragments into hundreds of pieces.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one shell may get 10 people, whereas a rifle bullet can only get one at a time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But a shell can get 10 or 15 people at a time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I would say during the war that probably 75% of all of our casualties and about 75% of all the German casualties were inflicted by artillery and mortars.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mortars have the same effect as artillery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you ever-- did your unit ever capture any German prisoners at that time?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we took prisoners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took the first prisoners in Sicily.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
